lished product that has consumer loyalty. Acquiring firms can also overcome econo
mies of scale entry barriers through buying a firm that has already successfully 
achieved economies of scale. In addition, acquisitions can often overcome barrier
s to entry into international markets. (3) }\plain \i \f1
\fs22
